Package com.stuypulse.stuylib.control

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    The controller class is an abstract class that is used to create different controllers.
    PIDCalculator
    This is a Bang-Bang controller that while controlling the robot, will be able to calculate the values for the PID controller.
    PIDController
    This PID controller is built by extending the Controller class.
    TBHController
    The take back half algorithm is one made specifically to help with controlling shooters.
